channel.title: Quick help on changing logout message
channel.description: Ok this is a simple question but i cant figure it out. When u go to logout and click the X in the top right conner and the logout button comes up. There is a message above the button that say something like "thanks for playing" i wanted to change what is says and i cant find where its located. Anyone have any ideas?
